    "date": "2019-11-08T16:46:42Z",
    "text": "Fly Smart Act\n\nThis bill establishes standards for\u00a0airline travel by federal employees for official business, including a\u00a0general requirement to use coach-class accommodations and a\u00a0ban on military aircraft for domestic official travel. It allows use of first-class and business class for federal employees under certain circumstances, such as to accommodate a disability or special need or because of exceptional security circumstances."
